{"tid":924769,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重用舊片？】央視宣傳黑龍江武警冬訓 網揭內容似曾相識","createTime":"2018-12-02T11:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T11:38:27.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8af2ab2a989b00b3c93e15bdba8ca3e1dc3b03e4","tid":924769,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【重用舊片？】央視宣傳黑龍江武警冬訓 網揭內容似曾相識</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181201/58979495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58979495&d=jWUPf6E296uzEMOVpP4tvOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=db5cd82c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58979495&h=00d88de9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181201/58979495</a><br />\n<br />\n央視近日宣傳黑龍江武警在冰天雪地訓練的情況，但有眼利的網民發現，今年的冬季大練兵竟然與年初公佈的片段出奇地相似。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，武警黑龍江總隊官兵展開抗嚴寒極限訓練，戰士們赤膊奔向雪地。特戰隊員毛武凱說，就是要做更難的訓練，練出血性虎氣。但有網民發現，武警在雪地練拳法跟片段一開始的武警，與今年年初的畫面一模一樣，不單止訓練的官兵，就接接受訪問的中隊長，也是同一人，受訪內容也是完全一樣。<br />\n<br />\n這兩條宣傳片分別在年初及近日播放，相差只有10個月，唯一分別只是多了一些攀山的訓練畫面。其實，黑龍江武警在雪地受訓的報道，是每年冬天官方媒體的熱門題目，只要在微博輸入關鍵字，就見到黑龍江武警冬訓的結果。"},{"pid":"9a273a4fac786649ad592c851c42683b6101c26b","tid":924769,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4da64e6a7910b48aeaec0b892d313c63a85f1da","tid":924769,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"同亞視一樣重播又重播。"},{"pid":"08452153790bb78388cb2ef209df99b5135e4bcd","tid":924769,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:38:27.000Z","msg":"警樂無窮"}]}